{"tid":543939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴黎水浸】塞納河氾濫240城鎮變澤國 羅浮宮底層要關閉","createTime":"2018-01-29T04:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:09:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68005efba5b5bfc82cd4eb0d693366a9adc7ac87","tid":543939,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180129/large/1517196196_0a51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180129%2Flarge%2F1517196196_0a51.jpg&h=19be54a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國巴黎暴雨成災，塞納河（River Seine）水位上漲，是自1900年以來，三大潮濕冬季之一，多達240個城鎮因洪水氾濫受破壞，約1500人被迫撤離家園，羅浮宮的底層亦要關閉。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎西部有城巿建築物底層水浸，居民要以船代車出入。巴黎的水上交通被禁，遊船公司蒙受損失；警方亦向在塞納河划獨木舟的人罰款，斥他們行為「不負責任」。另外，多間博物館，包括著名的奧賽美術館和橘園美術館也受到洪水威脅。<br />\n<br />\n當局處於高度戒備，塞納河水位在周六24小時間上升10厘米(4.3吋)，比平時的高3.9米(13呎)；當局估計水位會繼續上升，但相信嚴重程度不及2016年，當年水位上升6米（20呎）羅浮宮要關閉4天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180129/large/1517196197_83d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180129%2Flarge%2F1517196197_83d5.jpg&h=226961d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180129/large/1517196200_7b00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180129%2Flarge%2F1517196200_7b00.jpg&h=4241f516&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0f4c9d864b45c9c0c87e14d9b617ef2868c4ce0","tid":543939,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"香港己死 !"},{"pid":"ea1923f36f6aaa1ae8693a01e5282b83555335a5","tid":543939,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170710/_2017071017042823596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170710%2F_2017071017042823596.jpg&h=8a9d0c57&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}